				<%= image_tag("mat_v2.jpg") %>
			</div>
			<p style="text-align: center">
				<br>
				<iframe width="448" height="252"id="youtube" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/B_DJ-EEcN6c" title="YouTube video player"
								frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope;
						picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
				<br>
				Dr. Behnam Javanmardi presented Bone2Gene in the annual meeting of the German Society of Human Genetics
				2022 in Wuerzburg
			</p>
		</div>

